# Receipt photos → Supabase Storage (required on Vercel).
# 1. Run scripts/supabase-receipts-bucket.sql in Supabase SQL Editor (once).
# 2. Set on Vercel:
#    SUPABASE_URL="https://YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co"
#    SUPABASE_SECRET_KEY="sb_secret_..."   (or SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY for legacy JWT key)
